{"tid":2118040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚, 我喺元朗站附近撞到隊好古怪嘅狗","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T08:38:01.000Z","uid":362865,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e287b1cafc8575e150c0cd09f23349d581e9cb8f","tid":2118040,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"尋晚半夜收工返屋企, 過緊條明渠嗰陣覺得腳底有強烈嘅電流通過。我停低望一望, 見到渠口有鼓紫紫地若隱若現咁嘅煙, 隨後就有一隊Full gear Green Object行左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n行出前嗰個突然間指住我大叫：「細路, 你今年區選想投邊個啊！」<br />\n<br />\n「今年選立法會啊，啊好玩啦啊Sir！」我驚到腳震, 呆左喺到走都走唔到。<br />\n<br />\n「早左一年啊, 快手！ Go Go Go！」帶頭嗰個即刻推返後面班人入去個渠口, 佢臨入去之前停左一停, 調頭指住我講：「唔好放棄啊, 會贏架！」<br />\n<br />\n然後腳底再有一陣好強嘅電流通過, 下面就再冇任何聲氣....<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲我是咪撞邪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6836012a25f9433f938fde183451f257cf7a059d","tid":2118040,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adb80bf09af7d96889f400f01f9f487e6d1a17e","tid":2118040,"uid":32171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"你去講故台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4aa16df7bda9667f05d12ec2e339266bd232a54","tid":2118040,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會作落去？"},{"pid":"2d171b32cc787d66f94ed09349b2264a5f179c34","tid":2118040,"uid":362865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5adb80bf09af7d96889f400f01f9f487e6d1a17e","tid":2118040,"uid":32171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"你去講故台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}